HEADWORD: Maikel
<hw>Mai*kel"</hw> <pr>(m⟦aum⟧⟦icr⟧*k⟦asl⟧l")</pr>, <pos>n.</pos>
<fld>(Zool.)</fld> <def>A South American carnivore of the genus
<gen>Conepatus</gen>, allied to the skunk, but larger, and having a
longer snout. The tail is not bushy.</def>⟦br⟧
